                <h3>Game info</h3>
                <article>
                    <p>This is a text based gladiator game based on D&D rules.</p>
                    <p>You will be able to manage a stable of gladiators to fight with.</p>
                    <p>Game is based on a dice system and the dices range from a D4 to D20.</p>
                    <br />
                    <h4>Gladiator Stable</h4>
                    <p>A Player can only have a max of five gladiators in the stable.</p>
                    <p>Each gladiator earns Experiance, gold and score. The gold is used to heal your gladiator between fights.</p>
                    <p>A gladiator that runs out of both health and gold will be permantly dead.</p>
                    <br />
                    <h4>Highscore info</h4>
                    <p>You can compete with othere players on the highscore list.</p>
                    <p>There is two highscore lists one for the player highscore and one for gladiator highscore.</p>
                    @*Change this one incase i change back the player score*@
                    <p>The player highscore is calculated for each gladiator that currently on win streak when losing 
                     the score they have is removed from the players</p> 
                </article>
